  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Neha, I hope you had a good time at the Velvet Haze show — what did you end up doing that Friday?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Didn’t go. Last minute plans fell through. Was supposed to meet friends, but they canceled. Sat home doing nothing. Bored. Watched a movie. What’s your take on indie music?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Oh, that’s a bummer — movie nights are better with snacks and company. Indie music feels so personal, like the artist is singing just for you. What’s your favourite part about it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The intimacy, maybe? Or the rawness. Like, it feels more *real*. Not overproduced. But sometimes it’s too mellow for me. I prefer stuff with good beats. You know, something you can vibe to. What about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — some indie feels like a quiet chat while others are full of energy. I’m all for music that makes you tap your foot or sway a little. What kind of beats catch your attention?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Electronic beats. The ones that hit just right — you don’t think, you just move. Or lo-fi, when it’s chill but still groovy. But maybe I’m biased. I design products for a living, you know? So rhythm and flow matter. What’s your vibe?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That makes sense — design and music both need rhythm to feel right. I love when something flows without effort, like a good chai with just the right sugar. Smooth beats or smooth brews — what’s your pick?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Chai, hands down. No competition. But I mean, a good brew is a good brew. My chai needs cardamom, though — no ifs or buts. Speaking of, I need to get going. Found a new café downtown. Gotta test the vibes. Maybe next week. Bye."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it — cardamom chai is the best kind. New café, huh? Let me guess, you're checking the light, the layout, the vibe for design inspiration. Tell me how it goes next week!\""
    }
  ],
